Time to clear out some room in anticipation of 2015 purchases. Please PM me if interested. 

Prices are firm. I accept Check, MO, or Paypal (no fees). Please add $2 Shipping for a single card or free shipping for multiple card purchases ( I also have cards listed in the non-T206 1900-1919 section).

T206:
Sovereign 350 Huggins (portrait) SGC 20 (left edge is a bit chewed): $sold
Pied 350-460 Happy Smith BVG 2.5: (small paper loss on back) $sold
Pied 350-460 Josh Devore PSA 1.5: $sold

Southern Leaguers:

Old Mill Molesworth SGC 20 $sold
Old Mill Guiheen SGC 20 (discoloration) $sold
Old Mill Carey SGC 20 (small paper loss and writing on back) $sold
Pied 350 Ryan SGC 20 $40
Pied 350 Fritz SGC 20 (small paper loss on sleeve) $50
Pied 350 Kiernan SGC 10 (light pencil “c” in top right of front and “p” on the back): $sold
